com.hazelcast.map.impl.mapstore.writebehind

Interface WriteBehindQueue<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of element to be stored in this queue.

    public interface WriteBehindQueue<E>
    A specific queue implementation which is used for write-behind-store operations. Also supports filtering via filter(IPredicate, Collection)

    • Method Summary
